   About Cruz Bustamante
   _____________________________________________________________________

   Dear Friends,

   Welcome to my web site!

   I am very proud to be serving the people of the State of California as
   their 45th Lieutenant Governor. As you explore this site, you will find
   plenty of useful information, including my biography, the latest news
   from our office, my responsibilities as Lieutenant Governor,
   information about programs managed by my office, and links to other
   useful sites.

   Feel free to contact me and let me know what is on your mind.

   Enjoy the site and thank you for visiting!

   Cruz M. Bustamante
   CRUZ M. BUSTAMANTE
   Lieutenant Governor
